{"tid":594793,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"以三年為限，你覺得人生邊三年變化最大？","createTime":"2018-03-16T06:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T18:04:08.000Z","uid":15935,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ed96cac16bb221e1891e4a40a81ed7da77de0aa8","tid":594793,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T06:33:12.000Z","msg":"會唔會係18/19-21歲，覺得高中畢業同大學畢業時候嘅自己變得最多？<br />\n27/28歲個陣要為30出頭成家立室嘅事而煩惱同拼搏，覺得個社會迫你成熟？<br />\n定係35-38歲個陣開始對現實力不從心，唏噓同認命自己青春不再嘅時候？<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ec2b9dfea0fe42e31fb8ed681e8b9760278b2f","tid":594793,"uid":64017,"like":12,"dislike":10,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T07:08:56.000Z","msg":"1. 會考個幾年, O岩O岩14分夠升中六 (HKCEE)<br />\n<br />\n2. A-Level 第一次炒左, 再RETAKE又炒, 最後去做太空狗<br />\n<br />\n3. ASSO GPA差0.01先fulfil到poly account既undergrad offer, 最後我自己打去求programmer leader收我<br />\n<br />\n4. 大學yr1 sem1 GPA1.99, 收到warning, 點知 sem2 都係1.99, 要被kick out, 最後有個Korean Prof幫我改左一分, 最後appeal gpa 2.00, at the end 順利grad (唔知叫唔叫順利 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n5. 原本係間trustee on99做 fund admin, 有高人收去做risk and quant....(可能對大家無咩感覺, 但對我黎講係其中一樣改變我命運的事情)"},{"pid":"ea9f30a87f35d3a16c954359d962a2d18e205155","tid":594793,"uid":113000,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T07:10:05.000Z","msg":"頭三歲"},{"pid":"c3de520f9724cf6d59a37ab58666e78f46c488c5","tid":594793,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T07:17:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"910e0a989392836453e13be7dec58300e1b7e379","tid":594793,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c3de520f9724cf6d59a37ab58666e78f46c488c5","tid":594793,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea9f30a87f35d3a16c954359d962a2d18e205155","tid":594793,"uid":113000,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T07:10:05.000Z","msg":"頭三歲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T07:17:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T08:43:34.000Z","msg":"個陣未有意識嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f01723802ae7768d260ef18a8cf2e8577f2e48f9","tid":594793,"uid":113675,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T08:53:02.000Z","msg":"三年經歷親人過身, 分手, 畢業,搵工,再讀master<br />\n<br />\n令自己反思工作同讀書,甚至人生既意義<br />\n<br />\n用左二十幾年時間向其他人證明我唔係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n呢兩年慢慢唔想再同人證明D乜野<br />\n<br />\n想多D享受同自己相處，做自己想做既事就夠<br />\n<br />\n以前好多執著，當見證住身邊既人一個一個咁走<br />\n<br />\n反而放低左好多野"},{"pid":"b0bdeb47e42052ae76dcb8f75deb746141024fde","tid":594793,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T08:55:44.000Z","msg":"標準答案係你地收尾果三年<br />\n入醫院插晒喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c790526e835f04275b7a5a1ddaac40581841bb","tid":594793,"uid":148724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T08:57:31.000Z","msg":"27/28歲個陣要為30出頭成家立室嘅事而煩惱同拼搏，覺得個社會迫你成熟？<br />\n<br />\n呢句真<br />\n不過果種無力感真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f22c73c127cd4a7e37c5dec19b902ea2b7e4b9","tid":594793,"uid":148201,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T08:59:06.000Z","msg":"未考公開試到完左公開試，自己成熟左<br />\n再讀上去，又成熟左<br />\n住hall,又成熟左"},{"pid":"046cdad8caa41e16270eb45f034599359d9631b5","tid":594793,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f01723802ae7768d260ef18a8cf2e8577f2e48f9","tid":594793,"uid":113675,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T08:53:02.000Z","msg":"三年經歷親人過身, 分手, 畢業,搵工,再讀master<br />\n<br />\n令自己反思工作同讀書,甚至人生既意義<br />\n<br />\n用左二十幾年時間向其他人證明我唔係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n呢兩年慢慢唔想再同人證明D乜野<br />\n<br />\n想多D享受同自己相處，做自己想做既事就夠<br />\n<br />\n以前好多執著，當見證住身邊既人一個一個咁走<br />\n<br />\n反而放低左好多野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T09:09:06.000Z","msg":"短短幾年經歷咗咁多野 唔易過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0507d6022dd0dc18a06c3ab2511c57754ec0bd","tid":594793,"uid":113675,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"046cdad8caa41e16270eb45f034599359d9631b5","tid":594793,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f01723802ae7768d260ef18a8cf2e8577f2e48f9","tid":594793,"uid":113675,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T08:53:02.000Z","msg":"三年經歷親人過身, 分手, 畢業,搵工,再讀master<br />\n<br />\n令自己反思工作同讀書,甚至人生既意義<br />\n<br />\n用左二十幾年時間向其他人證明我唔係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n呢兩年慢慢唔想再同人證明D乜野<br />\n<br />\n想多D享受同自己相處，做自己想做既事就夠<br />\n<br />\n以前好多執著，當見證住身邊既人一個一個咁走<br />\n<br />\n反而放低左好多野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T09:09:06.000Z","msg":"短短幾年經歷咗咁多野 唔易過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T09:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人生就係咁奇妙<br />\n<br />\n幾年前畢業，我都係on99咁同ex plan緊搵工買樓結婚<br />\n<br />\n後尾咪又係散左<br />\n<br />\n一個人廿幾年黎好地地同你有講有笑，突然間幾個月之後你要去拜山先見到佢<br />\n<br />\n講出黎好輕鬆，但背後有幾多個眼淚，有幾多真係會明<br />\n<br />\n宜家唔想再為其他人而生活，可能會少左Ｄ朋友，但會放鬆開心好多"},{"pid":"7ad54eab4c0d8effae21cba5d0ba8b77cef8776d","tid":594793,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff0507d6022dd0dc18a06c3ab2511c57754ec0bd","tid":594793,"uid":113675,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"046cdad8caa41e16270eb45f034599359d9631b5","tid":594793,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f01723802ae7768d260ef18a8cf2e8577f2e48f9","tid":594793,"uid":113675,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T08:53:02.000Z","msg":"三年經歷親人過身, 分手, 畢業,搵工,再讀master<br />\n<br />\n令自己反思工作同讀書,甚至人生既意義<br />\n<br />\n用左二十幾年時間向其他人證明我唔係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n呢兩年慢慢唔想再同人證明D乜野<br />\n<br />\n想